# Network Architecture

## Overview

The Enterprise Network Design project is built around a modular architecture consisting of three independent logical networks:

- Corporate Office Network
- Home Network
- Internet Service Provider (ISP) Network

Each network serves a distinct purpose and is designed to simulate a real-world enterprise deployment while remaining scalable for future enhancements.


